{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">My Taskbar Farm is a minimalist idle farming simulator for your taskbar. Perfect for playing while you multitask on your PC.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326530/extras/Page_Desc_logo.png?t=1736151553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Raise Farm Animals</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start with a chicken and watch it lay eggs while you work. Unlock new animals as you progress, from adorable cows to fluffy sheep and truffle-hunting pigs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Automate and Build.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy drones to help with gathering resources. Upgrade your little bots for greater efficiency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Purchase aviaries and barns to free up space and focus production in one place. Upgrade buildings to collect and sell products automatically.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multitasking:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">My Taskbar Farm is designed to sit comfortably on your taskbar, letting you manage your farm while doing other tasks, all without demanding much of your attention.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Still not sure if this game is for you? It has colorful dinosaurs \u2014 that\u2019s right, <strong>COLORFUL DINOSAURS!</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326530/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736151553","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326530/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736151553","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326530/4fe98f6a0dd44ead9b5631aad068d7c6fcd3ac7e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736151553","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326530/4fe98f6a0dd44ead9b56